We will restore your car to better than like-new condition, remove every stain and protect your paint for YEARS
Welcome to INTENCE Detailing, your trusted premium quality car detailing specialist. We offer a total package of professional car detailing services. These services include the thorough cleaning, polishing, and protection of cars. Always with the goal to bring your car back to absolute showroom condition
Unlike traditional car detailing companies, we put quality above quantity. That's why you can trust us to treat your car with the utmost care. By using the best materials, products, and techniques, we achieve the best results. Whether you opt for a car coating, polishing treatment, interior cleaning, or another detailing service, INTENCE Detailing will transform your car into top condition! We provide comprehensive detailing services throughout Papakura, Karaka, Pukekohe, and surrounding areas, bringing showroom-quality results directly to you


